data.name: Botanic Healthcare
data.description: "Our legacy is 20 years of expertise and customer satisfaction, driven by revolutionary scientific methodologies and unswerving devotion to quality. We are today global leaders in developing and manufacturing plant-derived active principles for complementary health medicine: pharmaceuticals, health-food and personal care industries. We integrate traditional knowledge with modern science to create a path-breaking approach to natural health ingredients We believe wellness is a way of life. Led by eminent individuals who have dedicated their lives and work to botanical research, we are invested in staying ahead of the curve, understanding nutrient delivery mechanisms in the body and making world-class nutraceuticals accessible and affordable to everyone around the world. We continue to invest in research and development to create breakthrough products with a vision to enhance the life of every person who puts their trust in us. Driven by global standards, every member of the Botanic Healthcare team is committed to our quality procedures to ensure complete traceability of the ingredients we manufacture. We incorporate global best practices and multi-stage testing methods to validate the purity of our products. All our manufacturing units are cGMP, ISO, HACCP, Halal and Kosher certified."

data.name: AshwaMind
data.description: AshwaMind® is the world’s best ashwagandha product for memory and cognition enhancement. AshwaMind, made from ashwagandha (Withania somnifera) is a clinically tested, standardized and full spectrum extract containing six withanolides (withanoside IV, withaferin A, withoside VI, 12-deoxy withastramonolide, withanolide A and withanolide B) to support memory and cognitive abilities in adults. AshwaMind is manufactured using a unique extraction process, yielding the optimum percentage of withanolides, and retaining the plant’s other important bioactives, which are required for the efficacy of the herb.

data.name: Absocurcumin Power Booster
data.description: Absocurcumin is the natural curcumin extract formulated exclusively with enhanced bioavailability for maximum absorption and to meet body’s requirement. It also has anti- inflammatory and antioxidant properties that reduces the damage caused by free radicals. The antioxidants enhance immunity of the body. The nutrients in curcumin is highly beneficial in improving skin health and give you a youthful glowing skin. Curcumin supports the digestive system functions and helps the body to absorb nutrients effectively. It prevents excess acid formation in the gut and protects you from gas and bloating. It is a 100% pure organic vegetarian product with no added preservatives and pesticides.

data.name: TinoImmune
data.description: TinoImmune® is a high-concentration extract of Tinospora cordifolia. It is a clinically tested, standardized product that boosts immunity. Tinospora cordifolia and its constituent α-D-glucan stimulate Natural Killer (NK) Cells, B Cells, and T Cells while simultaneously producing various immune system-stimulating cytokines.

data.name: Absoperine
data.description: Absoperine® is the standardized extract obtained from dried unripe berries of Black pepper or Piper nigrum. Most commonly, known as King of Spices, pepper boosts taste and aroma of dishes. It can be used as a nutritional supplement to increase the bioavailability of herbal extracts such as curcumin. It acts by breaking down the fat in cells to increase the internal temperature (thermogenesis) which in turn increases the metabolism and absorptive functions.

data.name: MenoSphora
data.description: MenoSphora® is a clinically tested, standardized, and full-spectrum extract containing sophoricoside to support the bone health of menopausal women. Sopohiricoside is an extract of Sophora japonica, a plant commonly used to improve the circulatory system. It has a documented history of being used to promote optimal vein health and it’s one of the 50 fundamental herbs in traditional Chinese medicine. Sophora extract supports menopausal women with its phytoestrogen supplement properties and promotes physical comfort and mood balance. It also helps support osteoporosis and strengthens bones.

data.name: Botanic Healthcare Palmarosa Oil
data.description: Obtained by steam distillation process, Palmarosa Oil possesses anti-bacterial, antifungal and antiviral properties that make the oil an excellent choice in aromatherapies, food, beverage, pharmaceutical, cosmetic, personal care and so forth applications. If you are looking for one of the best Palmarosa Oil Manufacturers in India for placing bulk orders, Botanic Healthcare is undeniably the one you can reach without any second thoughts.

data.name: Botanic Healthcare Ginger Extract Powder
data.description: Botanic Healthcare is one of the best Ginger Extract Powder Manufacturers in India, committed to meeting diverse requirements for herbal extracts and more. Being processed hygienically at our in-house facility under strict supervision, Ginger Extract Powder contains natural properties. It is free from additives, chemicals and other contaminants and ensures better safety in the long run.

data.name: Botanic Healthcare Asparagus Extract
data.description: Being counted amongst the best Asparagus Extract Manufacturers in India, Botanic Healthcare offer pure Asparagus Extracts. Used for treating many health ailments, like female rejuvenation, infertility and libido enhancement, Asparagus Extracts cure menopausal problems and balance hormone levels. The healing capacity of the herb increases its participation in various medicinal applications.

data.name: Botanic Healthcare Bambusa Arundinacea (Vanshlochan)
data.description: Botanic Healthcare has become one of the highly acclaimed Bambusa Arundinacea (Vanshlochan) Manufacturers in India. Prepared with a scientific approach combined with the core concept of Ayurveda, Bambusa Arundinacea Extract helps cure various skin problems and is used widely for manufacturing skin medicines.

data.name: Botanic Healthcare Guggul Extract
data.description: Botanic Healthcare is one of the prominent Guggul Extract Manufacturers in India engaged in offering hygienically processed Guggul Extract in numerous forms and quantities. Extracted from the gum resins of the Commiphora Mukul tree, native to India, Guggul Extracts are noted for its healing properties of balancing cholesterol, curing arthritis pain and curing other skin diseases.

data.name: Botanic Healthcare Kava Extract
data.description: Botanic Healthcare - one of the well-renowned Kava Extract Manufacturers in India, process the extract following USFDA, TGA, MEDSAFE and EU guidelines to keep the quality, purity and effectiveness intact. We have an advanced manufacturing unit loaded with developed machinery that helps us maintain hygiene and bulk processing within a promised time frame.

data.name: Botanic Healthcare Magnesium
data.description: Plant-Based Minerals are free from adulterants and safe for making different products. We implement our extensive manufacturing expertise and innovative technology to meet superior quality standards. We have the capabilities and expertise to support you every step of the way.

data.name: Botanic Healthcare Amla Extract
data.description: Botanic Healthcare - one of the worlds’ recognized Amla Extract Manufacturers in India brings Amla Extract containing 10% to 50% tannins by UV. Being a powerhouse of nutrients and vitamins, Amla is a highly revered plant, having an extensive role in Ayurveda to balance all three Doshas. It nowadays has a huge demand in pharmaceutical industries, which we satisfy with our continuous delivery.
